reviewText:
Victory in 1 hour on hard difficulty and no intentions for replay. Uncle Sid, you sold me a prealfa? Where is the game of famous Sid Meier with “please, one more turn” and 100% replayability? Civ I was much better! It’s the second unfinished game you selling to people:
1)	Absolutely unbalanced (purity against other bonuses);
2)	No description of damage mechanics;
3)	Strange science prices without any explanation (“+25% shield” 25% of what? That’s the base value?)
4)	Idiotic AI without any diplomacy;
5)	Overpowered torpedoes;
6)	I can write 10 items more.

Uncle Sid, please, send me the link for the real Game!
